TITLE: Signing and Encrypting Session Data in Ktor
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to sign and encrypt session data using SessionTransportTransformerEncrypt. It includes setting up encryption keys and configuring the session cookie.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ktorio/ktor-documentation/blob/main/topics/server-sessions.md#2025-04-09_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: kotlin
CODE:
```
install(Sessions) {
    cookie<UserSession>("user_session") {
        cookie.path = "/"
        cookie.maxAgeInSeconds = 60
        transform(SessionTransportTransformerEncrypt(
            encryptionKey = hex("00112233445566778899aabbccddeeff"),
