TITLE: Building the Ktor Middleware Application
DESCRIPTION: Command to build the Ktor application that demonstrates custom middleware implementation. This should be executed from the project's root directory.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ktorio/ktor-documentation/blob/main/codeSnippets/snippets/migrating-express-ktor/8_middleware/README.md#2025-04-09_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: shell
CODE:
```
./gradlew build
```
